      "text": "（観客席の私達が見守る中、ステージでは）\n（琴乃ちゃん達が勝利後のインタビューを受けていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As we watch from the audience‚ on the stage‚)\n(Kotono and her team are being interviewed after their victory.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 9.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 9.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-host001.m4a",
      "text": "これでベスト8進出ですが\n次のステージに向けて、抱負をどうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This advances you into the Top 8.\nPlease tell us your ambitions for your next performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 15.395402187040482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。次も全力で頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. We will go full-throttle in our next performance‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.395402187040482,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3571.2644796261834,
          "startTime": 18.966666666666665
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-host002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、この得点ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you just look at that score!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.397352212598957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 21.897352212599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い声援……\nこれ、みんな、琴乃ちゃん達への声援？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen to the crowd scream!\nAre they all screaming for Kotono’s group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.61616183313831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "当然……\nだって、あれだけの点数だったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nLook how high they scored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.97686917973663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "（月のテンペストの点数は、LizNoirさんや）\n（TRINITYAiLEさんを上回るものだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Moon Tempest’s score exceeded the scores)\n(of LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "（大会レコードを出した二つの優勝候補より）\n（さらに高い点数を、琴乃ちゃん達は出したのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They were the two favorites to win‚ who’d just set new tournament records.)\n(And Kotono’s group scored even higher than them.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.13539536191128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.268349807663476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "大切なのは勝つことよ\n点数じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Winning is what’s important.\nNot the score.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 53.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、点数で上を行く必要はない）\n（大切なのは勝ち進むこと。勝ち進んで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(True. You don’t need points to climb to the top.)\n(What’s important is to win. To keep winning and…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 61.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……\n私達の明日の相手って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but…\nTomorrow‚ we’re up against…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 66.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……バンプロダクションの有望株\nリズノワ、トリエルに次ぐ実力のDayDream",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…one of Van Productions’ promising groups.\nDayDream‚ with talent equal to LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "けっして、あなどれないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We definitely can’t underestimate them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 76.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 76.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 82.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "（ステージでは、琴乃ちゃんが観客席に手を振っている）\n（まるで何かから解放されたような、楽しそうな笑顔）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(On stage‚ Kotono is waving to the audience.)\n(Her smile is so carefree as if she’s been released from something.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 86.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "（その笑顔を見ると、良かったと思うと同時に）\n（きゅっと心臓が締め付けられるような気がした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When I see her smile‚ a part of me feels happy for her.)\n(But I also feel like my heart is being squeezed.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 96.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 96.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 98.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "（見えるはずはない。けど私は）\n（琴乃ちゃんに見えるように、大きく手を振り返す）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I know she can’t see me. But I raise my hand high)\n(and wave back‚ hoping Kotono will see me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 107.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 107.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（さくら達五人が対戦相手、DayDreamの）\n（ステージ映像を見ている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sakura and her team are watching performance footage of DayDream‚)\n(the group they’ll be competing against.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、あのバンプロダクションが\n育てたアイドルね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s Van Productions for you.\nThey sure know how to train idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "プロのレッスンをただ受けているだけでは\nこの動きは出来ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t get that good at dancing\njust by getting lessons from a pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "目線の動かし方……\nそれに観客の盛り上げ方……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way they move their eyes‚\nand the way they hype up the crowd…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワやトリエルを参考にしつつ\nでも全部、自分達のものにしている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re clearly influenced by LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE‚\nyet they’ve made everything their own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "デビューは、トリエルよりも前……\nキャリアは結構長い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They debuted earlier than TRINITYAiLE.\nThey’ve had a pretty long career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "勝てる……かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you think… we can beat them?",
